              <span class="chevron">⌄</span>
            </button>
            <div class="accordion-panel" data-accordion-panel>
              <p>Yes! You can upgrade or downgrade your plan at any time. Upgrades take effect immediately, while downgrades apply at the start of your next billing cycle. Unused AI credits don't roll over when changing plans.</p>
